philosophy, the discoveries.

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:54.020
The discoveries of diseases,
and so on and so forth.

00:03:54.020 --> 00:04:00.770
There is, in this institution,
there is a part of every corner

00:04:00.770 --> 00:04:03.230
